{"tid":635259,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美財政部研緊急權力 將對中國投資永久設限","createTime":"2018-04-20T03:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T01:26:42.000Z","uid":13663,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1727e098d3d394f07569e7a21948f16bc6e8df","tid":635259,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:52:22.000Z","msg":"美國財政部官員表示，可能行使緊急情況下取得的權力，限制中國公司在美國的投資。<br />\n<br />\n美國財政部負責國際市場與投資的助理財長Heath Tarbert出席國際金融論壇時指出，根據301條款，總統特朗普政府可以根據國家安全為理由，實施緊急權力，限制中國公司的投資。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問及財政部是否提出立法改變外國投資法，或使用國際緊急經濟權力法例時，他表示一個專責研究中國投資的財政部分支正考慮有關事宜，但上述兩項考慮是由兩分支各自研究的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1821778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1821778&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRADACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=e4a04723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1821778</a>"},{"pid":"164916171ccf9a7de2409a74763465ef9e935b2c","tid":635259,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"越玩越大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ba51c5c4abb0b218befde008f52cc88f5df533","tid":635259,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a4c2c8d92f8de996f4b671660f81ccd227aac0","tid":635259,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:58:17.000Z","msg":"而家大陸好被動<br />\n話說而家d五毛好似收晒皮既<br />\n冇晒糧出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"2a21a413e20d9c46431f203d0dc56a05a8f54c41","tid":635259,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"股災近了"},{"pid":"688a71d64e07bb0e4be38da108c0670fb04b0d21","tid":635259,"uid":143572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"包唔包腥港先"},{"pid":"1b0ebe20424b77e9196ee5f502b6bdc8423fc8f3","tid":635259,"uid":180404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"即係又跌呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253c873460e38c0709be43db24f338ea130638a0","tid":635259,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:05:28.000Z","msg":"快d"},{"pid":"d0d7ca6fe64be391ea590da5589fe70e4699b1a9","tid":635259,"uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:07:09.000Z","msg":"據《彭博》報導，美國財政部正考慮使用一項緊急法律，來限制中國對敏感技術的投資，川普政府希望藉此懲罰中國侵犯美國智財權的行為。<br />\n<br />\n財政部國際事務辦公室助理秘書 Heath Tarbert 表示，美國政府正評估《國際緊急經濟權力法案》(International Emergency Economic Powers Act) 的可能使用情況。根據這項 1977 年的立法，在應對「不尋常和非常的威脅」時，總統可以宣布國家緊急狀況，並阻止交易與扣押資產。<br />\n<br />\n川普正敦促他的團隊，打擊他認為中國不公平的貿易行為，並威脅要對中國徵收高達 1500 億美元的關稅。此外，他也要求財長梅努欽 (Steven Mnuchin)，向中國公司進行投資限制，在 5 月 21 日前提出執行細節。<br />\n<br />\n目前投資人主要關注川普的關稅計畫，不過如果推出新的限制，中國對美的投資將因而減少，進而傷害美國公司籌資能力，打擊企業估值。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士指出，財政部正擬定計畫，以確定中國企業無法投資那些美國科技業，如半導體及 5G 通訊。此外，也預計施加更嚴格的條件，以國家安全為由，審查中國企業的投資。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a76ea4323ef838fce042cb301f20c4bd163488","tid":635259,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f7b42fe8c434b85a28633fc1b280cfa232dab4","tid":635259,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:20:31.000Z","msg":"又話抵抗美帝霸權 又跪係度唔做野 大國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9760bc316a16211d4688e1d922a0ab97e835fead","tid":635259,"ui